<topic id="ch_avoiding_page_breaks">
  <title>Avoiding Page Breaks</title>
  <body>
    <p>Sometimes page breaks should be avoided. For instance, to avoid breaking between a title and
      the subsequent content: </p>
    <codeblock outputclass="language-css">h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
    page-break-after: avoid;
}</codeblock>
    <p>Or if you want to avoid breaks inside tables and lists:</p>
    <p>
      <codeblock outputclass="language-css">table, ol, ul {
    page-break-inside: avoid;
}</codeblock>
    </p>
  </body>
</topic>
